comments.body:
Rebased.

@baude #2113 has made `imageParts` public via `DecomposeString`. Given the very dubious value of `tag`, and that the output of `DecomposeString` was not really used anywhere, I have just removed/reverted that part in here.

Feel free to make that public again, but (even if I’m too scared to just drop all existing uses outright)., any net new users of the `tag` value which can go `"none"` should IMHO come with a very strong and documented rationale.
